WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.720
Healthy food and drink for children.

00:03.720 --> 00:07.920
Is your food and drink healthy?

00:07.920 --> 00:15.920
A lot of ice cream, hamburgers and cola is not healthy.

00:15.920 --> 00:23.000
Meat is healthy, but too much meat is not good for children.

00:23.560 --> 00:32.680
Cola and candy are very sweet and too much sugar is bad for you.

00:32.680 --> 00:37.000
Eat the right food and be healthy.

00:37.000 --> 00:44.520
Carrots, eggs and sweet potatoes are good for your eyes.

00:44.520 --> 00:51.000
Milk, cheese and fish are good for your teeth.

00:51.000 --> 00:57.720
A bit tired? Have lots of delicious chicken soup.

00:57.720 --> 01:07.720
It is important to remember. Eat well, stay healthy and don't get fat.

01:07.720 --> 01:13.400
Eat noodles or rice, not hamburgers.

01:13.400 --> 01:17.560
Have a good breakfast every morning.

01:17.560 --> 01:25.160
Drink juice, water, tea and milk, not cola.

01:25.160 --> 01:29.960
Eat lots of fruit and vegetables.

